[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0405","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0405.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0218","title":"Livingston Portmaster 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Livingston Portmaster 远程访问服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标设备发送一系列特制命令，导致设备异常重启，造成正常服务中断。该漏洞影响 Livingston 多款 Portmaster 型号，攻击者只需网络可达即可触发，利用难度较低。厂商已发布修复固件，建议升级至最新版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0218"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.173","remediation":"立即升级至 Livingston/Lucent 发布的最新固件版本（若设备尚在运行且厂商已停止支持，则无官方补丁可用）。作为临时缓解措施，在边界防火墙或路由器 ACL 中限制对 Portmaster 管理端口（Telnet 23/SSH/SNMP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 段连接；同时禁用不必要的远程管理协议（如 Telnet），改用带外管理方式，并严格限制未授权的网络命令输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0218","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0218","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0218.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/713.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0218.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0405.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0430","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0430.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0245","title":"Linux NIS+ 认证绕过漏洞","description":"Linux NIS+（网络信息服务）在特定配置下存在认证绕过漏洞。当 NIS+ 配置文件中包含\"+\"通配符条目时，系统会将 NIS 映射中的用户信息直接导入本地认证数据库，导致攻击者无需有效凭据即可利用该通配符以任意用户身份登录系统。此漏洞源于 NIS+ 访问控制配置不当，攻击者只需具备本地网络访问权限即可触发，成功利用后可获得受影响系统的未授权访问，进而可能泄露敏感信息或进行后续攻击。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 发行版中启用 NIS+ 服务且未正确限制通配符条目的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0245"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1995-09-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.490","remediation":"升级到受支持的现代 Linux 发行版（如 RHEL 9、Ubuntu 22.04+），该漏洞仅在早期 NIS+ 配置中存在，现代版本已修复。检查并移除 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow、/etc/group 中的单独 \"+\" 通配符条目，将其替换为特定用户或组的显式映射。建议迁移至 LDAP 或 Kerberos 替代 NIS+ 身份验证体系，并在 /etc/hosts.allow 中限制 NIS 相关服务访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0245"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0430.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0323","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0323.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0155","title":"Artifex Ghostscript -dSAFER 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Ghostscript PostScript 解释器在启用 -dSAFER 安全选项时存在沙箱绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可构造特制的 PostScript 文件（如嵌入恶意 .eps 或 .ps 图片的文档），诱导用户或服务端程序解析即可触发，绕过 -dSAFER 对文件读写、命令执行等危险操作的限制，在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞广泛影响各类 Ghostscript 发行版，常见于图像处理、文档转换服务调用中，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0155"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:43.100","remediation":"升级 Ghostscript 至 9.50 及以上版本（SAFER 模式默认启用且大幅增强），使用 `-dSAFER` 参数运行。在无法升级时，结合 seccomp-bpf 或 AppArmor/SELinux 策略限制 Ghostscript 进程的文件读写和命令执行权限，避免直接处理来源不可信的 PostScript/PDF 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0155"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0323.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0335","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0335.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0164","title":"Sun Solaris ps 命令竞争条件漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中 `ps` 命令存在竞态条件漏洞，当该命令在处理文件时未正确同步对共享资源的访问，导致本地攻击者可通过精心构造的竞争访问条件在特定时间窗口内覆写或破坏系统中的关键文件。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 操作系统多个版本，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用此漏洞，可能导致系统文件损坏或服务异常。CVSS 评分为 6.2，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0164"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1995-08-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:44.273","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 官方针对 Solaris ps 命令竞争条件漏洞的安全补丁（对应 Sun 安全公告 00117 或后续累积补丁）。对于已停止官方支持的 Solaris 版本，应限制本地用户对系统的交互式登录权限，并启用审计日志监控 `ps` 命令的异常调用行为。建议升级至不受影响的 Solaris 版本或迁移至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11 以上版本。作为深度防御措施，可配置 RBAC（基于角色的访问控制）限制敏感文件的写权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/8346"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0335.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0388","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0388.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0203","title":"Sendmail Sendmail SMTP 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"tags, so I'll provide my final answer within those tags.<value>Sendmail 存在远程命令执行漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 SMTP 协议向目标服务器发送特制邮件，在 \"mail from\" 字段中填入恶意程序路径，同时构造无效的 \"rcpt to\" 地址触发邮件退回机制。当邮件系统处理退信时，会以 root 权限执行 \"mail from\" 中指定的程序，导致攻击者在无需认证的情况下获得目标主机的完全控制权限。该漏洞影响 Sendmail 及基于其代码的衍生邮件服务，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级为严重，属于经典的邮件服务远程提权漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0203"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-08-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:54.237","remediation":"升级 sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本，该版本默认禁止 SMTP 直接投递到程序并强化了地址校验。如无法升级，在 sendmail.cf 中设置 `O PrivacyOptions=restrictmailq,restrictqrun,noexpn,novrfy` 并重启服务作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0203"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0388.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0343","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0343.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0172","title":"Matt Wright FormMail CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"FormMail CGI 程序是一款广泛使用的 Perl 表单处理脚本，存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可在无需认证的情况下，通过向 FormMail 脚本发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用其对用户输入参数过滤不严的缺陷，注入并执行任意系统命令。该漏洞可导致服务器被完全控制、敏感信息泄露或被用作跳板发动进一步攻击。影响运行该脚本的所有 Web 服务器版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0172"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-08-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.293","remediation":"立即删除或禁用服务器上所有 Matt Wright 原版 FormMail.pl 脚本（通常位于 /cgi-bin/ 目录），替换为安全维护的分支版本如 NMS FormMail 或 FormMail Clone。如仍需使用，务必升级到最新的 FormMail 1.92 版本（已修复此漏洞），并限制可以接收邮件的收件人域名范围（$recipient_domain 配置项），移除调试开关 $debugging 设置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0172"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0343.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0330","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0330.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0161","title":"Cisco IOS 访问控制列表绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 10.3 在配置 tacacs-ds 或 tacacs 关键字时，扩展 IP 访问控制列表（ACL）存在过滤绕过漏洞。当使用 TACACS+ 认证的扩展 ACL 规则应用于接口时，系统未能正确匹配数据包与规则条目，导致实际生效的过滤策略与配置不符。远程攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过 ACL 限制，未经授权访问受保护的网络资源。该漏洞影响运行 Cisco IOS 10.3 的设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0161"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-07-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:43.920","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.0 及以上版本，避免使用已废弃的 tacacs-ds/tacacs 关键词，改用 tacacs+ 协议。配置访问控制列表时确保标准 ACL 与扩展 ACL 规则顺序正确，避免过滤绕过。在无法升级的环境中，移除使用缺陷关键词的 ACL 条目，改用基于命名或标准 ACL 的替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/797"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0330.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0165","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0165.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0066","title":"John S. Roberts AnyForm CGI 参数分号注入远程命令执行漏洞","description":"John S.2 Roberts AnyForm 1.0/2.0 是一款 CGI 表单处理程序，其存在远程命令执行漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过在 CGI 参数中插入分号（;）注入恶意系统命令，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 AnyForm 1.0 和 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0066"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1995-07-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.853","remediation":"立即停止使用 AnyForm CGI 脚本，删除或禁用服务器上所有 anyform.cgi/AnyForm 相关 CGI 程序。此软件已停止维护且不再更新，建议替换为支持输入过滤的现代表单处理方案，或迁移至 WSGI/FastCGI 架构以隔离 CGI 执行环境。如无法替换，在网络层面限制 CGI 目录的执行权限并禁用分号作为参数分隔符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/719","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19557","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0066","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0066.md","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-0066_0f0c3530-7572-4860-a943-991d78115c24","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/AnyForm.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/vicentewncosta/CVE/blob/f53f621dd0bde68d4b3c8ad5314ae2c5a0197af8/DOCUMENTATION.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0165.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0165.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0165.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0313","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0313.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0151","title":"SATAN 会话密钥泄露漏洞","description":"SATAN（Security Analysis Tool for Auditing Networks）安全审计工具的 Web 界面存在会话密钥泄露漏洞。当用户在使用 SATAN 分析工具的同时通过 Web 浏览器访问其他恶意站点时，攻击者可通过跨站请求等方式窃取 SATAN 的会话密钥，进而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 SATAN 工具，攻击条件为用户在运行 SATAN 时浏览了攻击者控制的网站，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0151"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-04-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.540","remediation":"CVE-1999-0151 年代久远，SATAN 工具已停止维护，**根本修复方案是停止使用 SATAN**，迁移至 Nessus、OpenVAS 等现代漏洞扫描器。若临时使用 SATAN Web 界面，应采取以下缓解措施：(1) 使用独立浏览器/配置文件运行 SATAN 界面，切勿在 SATAN 会话期间访问其他网站，防止 Referer 泄露 session key；(2) 配置浏览器或代理插件（如 Referer Control）在访问 SATAN 界面时禁止发送 Referer 头；(3) 在防火墙/主机层面限制运行 SATAN 的机器出站连接至外部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0151"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0313.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0427","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0242","title":"Slackware Linux POP3 邮件文件未授权访问漏洞","description":"部分 Linux 系统（如 Slackware）的 POP3 邮件服务存在认证绕过漏洞，当系统启用影子密码（shadow passwords）时，POP3 守护进程未能正确验证用户凭证，远程攻击者无需有效账号即可通过 POP3 协议访问目标系统上的邮件文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击复杂度低，危害较大。受影响系统包括使用 shadow passwords 机制的早期 Linux 发行版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0242"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.133","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 的 POP3 守护进程 (如 popper) 到已修复版本，或禁用 POP3 服务改用 IMAP+SSL。确保 /etc/shadow 文件权限为 400 且仅 root 可读，避免使用未加密的 POP3 协议传输密码。如系统已不再维护，建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80898/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0420","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0420.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0235","title":"NCSA httpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA httpd 1.4.1 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标 Web 服务器发送特制请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，攻击者利用此漏洞可完全控制受影响系统，危害严重。目前官方已停止维护该软件，建议用户升级至其他受支持的 Web 服务器软件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0235"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.270","remediation":"NCSA httpd 已停止维护多年，官方不再发布安全更新。建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server（最新稳定版为 2.4.68），该服务器由 NCSA httpd 衍生而来，兼容原有配置且持续提供安全支持。迁移后注意关闭不必要的 CGI 脚本并配置最低权限运行服务进程以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0235","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0235","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0235.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-73j6-752c-7hrj/GHSA-73j6-752c-7hrj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ed289855-2ebf-495d-9754-266d2c9ea1e7.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0420.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0417","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0232","title":"NCSA HTTPD 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 版本在处理 HTTP 请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送超长或特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致远程代码执行或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，且无需认证即可利用。由于该软件已停止维护，建议用户迁移至 Apache httpd 等受支持的 Web 服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0232"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.893","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至活跃维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制对 80/TCP 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83083/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0189","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0189.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0077","title":"Linux Kernel 2.2 TCP 初始序列号可预测漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2 版本 TCP 协议栈存在 TCP 初始序列号（ISN）可预测漏洞，远程攻击者可通过预测目标系统 TCP 连接的初始序列号，伪造 TCP 数据包实施会话劫持或欺骗攻击，导致未经授权的数据访问或服务中断。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.2 系列内核，攻击者只需掌握目标连接的序列号生成规律即可利用，无需身份认证。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0077"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.603","remediation":"建议升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.26 以上版本，或迁移至 2.4.x/2.6.x 系列内核以获得 RFC 1948 TCP ISN 随机化支持。如无法升级内核，可通过 `echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/tcp_syncookies` 启用 SYN Cookies 缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/139"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0189.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0393","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0393.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0207","title":"Majordomo 邮件列表管理 lists 命令远程执行漏洞","description":"Majordomo 1.89/1.90 及更早版本存在命令执行漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向邮件列表服务器发送特制邮件，在 Reply-To 字段中嵌入恶意 \"lists\" 命令参数，利用该漏洞在目标系统上以邮件服务器进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Majordomo 邮件列表管理软件，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0207"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1994-06-09","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Majordomo 至 1.94 或更高版本，该版本已修复通过 Reply-To 字段注入 lists 命令参数的远程命令执行漏洞。若无法升级，应在 wrappers 配置中限制 lists 命令执行权限，并严格过滤邮件头中特殊字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0207","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20597"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0393.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0393.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0556","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0337","title":"IBM AIX batch queue (bsh) 本地和远程权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统的批处理队列（bsh）存在权限提升漏洞。当网络打印服务启用时，本地或远程攻击者可通过向批处理队列提交特制任务，利用不充分的权限控制机制获取超出授权的系统访问权限，导致攻击者能够执行任意命令或操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 AIX 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0337"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.850","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 针对 AIX batch queue (bsh) 的安全补丁，升级到 AIX 4.3.3 及更高修复版本。如无法打补丁，可通过 `chsubserver -r bsh` 禁用 bsh 网络打印服务，或在 `/etc/security/user` 中限制 bsh 可执行权限仅为 root 用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0337.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Wollny/CVE-1999-0337.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000050.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6dd5b793-7342-42d5-867d-37abc515d322.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml"}]